            "title": "Our Story",
            "size_text": "h2",
            "text": "",
            "answer_content": "<p>Fleuriation was birthed from a mother navigating the unexpected challenges of developmental delays and eczema. She found herself desperate for answers and for a deeper understanding of what true wellness meant. That search led her to a life-changing discovery of non-toxic living and medicinal herbs. Through her discovery, she desired to create something pure, purposeful, and restorative. This led to the creation of Fleuriation. At the heart of Fleuriation is a belief inspired by Genesis 1:29, that God, in His wisdom, has provided plants and herbs as gifts for our nourishment and restoration. We honor this provision by crafting handmade batches of non-toxic and sustainable solutions that promote both skin health and internal vitality. Our products are formulated with high-quality organic and all-natural ingredients, enhanced with herbal-infused components. Our skin is our body’s largest organ, and what we put on our skin is just as important as what we eat. Fleuriation is more than just skincare; it is a symbol of hope for every person and family seeking non-toxic and high-quality plant-based products.</p>",
            "style_btn": "btn-underline btn-underline-white",
            "button": "",
            "link": "",
            "enable_padding": true,
            "align": "left"
          }
        }
