            "title": "Medicinal Herbs",
            "size_text": "h2",
            "text": "",
            "answer_content": "<p>We embrace the medicinal properties and the restorative power of herbs and plants. For centuries, herbs have been used to promote healing, restoration, and vitality, offering nature’s own remedies for skin and body wellness. Each herb we use is intentionally chosen for its unique therapeutic properties, whether to soothe irritation, support cell renewal, or protect the skin from environmental stressors. These botanicals work synergistically to nourish the body by addressing the root of skin concerns rather than masking them. Based on the combined insights of traditional herbal knowledge and modern research, we harness the potency of God-given herbs to create formulas that bring restoration and lasting results naturally.</p>",
            "style_btn": "btn-underline btn-underline-white",
            "button": "",
            "link": "",
            "enable_padding": true,
            "align": "left"
          }
        }
