            "bgtext": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "Heart of Fleuriation",
            "size_text": "h2",
            "text": "Hi there! I'm Katia, the heart and hands behind Fleuriation. This journey began when I witnessed the profound difference nature-crafted skincare made for my children. I felt called to create products with the finest herbal ingredients and turn it into a mission that cares for others with purity and purpose.   At Fleuriation, our mission is to formulate high-quality, all-natural, and organic herb-infused skincare and wellness products to restore and replenish the body. Integrity and transparency guide everything we do as we provide individuals and families with pure, plant-based products they can trust. Whether I'm at local events, connecting with families, or blending herbs in the studio, my intention is always the same: to offer products that honor God's creation and bring more peace and nourishment to your daily skin routine.  Fleuriation has grown in beautiful ways, but it will always remain deeply personal. Every product is something I truly believe in, crafted with prayer, purpose, and love. I believe you'll feel that in every jar, bottle, and bar.    With Gratitude,  Katia",
            "answer_content": "",
